metadata.name: Enchanted Forest
metadata.description:
Fairies live in the deep in the wood where no man has gone. These creatures like to sing song and dance. Even if they do something, they always sing at the same time. This fairy saw nice spider’s web. She decided to weave the web into a single strand for an amazing new dress.  
While she doesn’t notice a big spider hidden tree trunk. But she isn’t as simple as it looks at first glance. And spider should be afraid its guest.
